data.description: "Back on market due to the buyer's financing falling through!"  Charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in scenic Pasco County. Built in 1973, this delightful residence boasts timeless character and modern comforts. Revel in outdoor living with a captivating in-ground pool, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The home also features a convenient one-car garage and a fully fenced yard, ensuring privacy and security. Recent updates include a new roof and HVAC system, both installed within the last four years, providing peace of mind for years to come. Whether you're seeking a tranquil retreat or a place to gather with friends, this well-maintained property offers the best of Florida living. Don't miss your chance to own this gem!
